  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dba\u0da7\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "SLFP has more advantages in forming the next government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the current situation in the country, there are signs that any election will be held soon and an alliance led by the SLFP will have the greatest advantage in forming the next government, said the party chairman of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party, former President Maithripala Sirisena.",
        "The former president also mentioned that 42 MPs who represented the ruling party had to sit in the opposition and become independent because the majority of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna is not ready to work together for the country.",
        "Mr. Maithripala Sirisena said that forming an alliance with the left progressive political camp and forming a government will be mandatory in the future and he also said that he will request the party organizers to immediately start reconciliation work by including the disgruntled Pohottu members.",
        "The former president said this while addressing the party's 71st anniversary celebrations held today (2) at the Maharagama Youth Council Auditorium.",
        "This year's party anniversary celebration was organized under the theme 'Let us give life to our character - Let us take up the challenge - Let us shoulder the mission of the era'.",
        "The former president, who said that if Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, who had fallen to nothing, could become the president, it was impossible for the Sri Lanka Freedom Party to rise again, he also said that the former president has the ability to win again."
      ],
